Third-party assets bundled with ha-pimoroni-unicorn
====================================================

Weather icons
-------------
The 16x16 and 32x32 weather icons in firmware/engine/weather_icons.py are derived
from "weather-pixel-icons" by Dhole:

    https://github.com/Dhole/weather-pixel-icons

Licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
(CC BY-SA 4.0): https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

The original monochrome XBM bitmaps were converted to bit-packed row masks by
scripts/gen_weather_icons.py; the 8x8 set is hand-drawn. These derivatives remain
under CC BY-SA 4.0. Changes: format conversion (XBM -> packed rows) and addition of
an 8x8 size. CC BY-SA 4.0 material may be used within this GPLv3 project under the
GPLv3 compatibility provision of CC BY-SA 4.0.
